ayed home.", "ja": "「とても〜なので…」(名詞つき)。"}], "blank": {"before": "It was ", "after": " a cold day that we stayed home.", "options": ["such", "so", "very", "too"], "answer": "such", "ja": "「とても〜なので…」(名詞つき)。", "explain": {"answer": "such", "why": "such + a + 形容詞 + 名詞 + that。", "opts": {}}}}, {"id": "gxf_11", "title": "too ... to", "ja": "「〜すぎて…できない」。", "level": "B1", "examples": [{"en": "The box is too heavy to lift.", "ja": "「〜すぎて…できない」。"}], "blank": {"before": "The box is ", "after": " heavy to lift.", "options": ["too", "so", "very", "such"], "answer": "too", "ja": "「〜すぎて…できない」。", "explain": {"answer": "too", "why": "too ... to = 否定的結果。", "opts": {}}}}, {"id": "gxf_12", "title": "enough to", "ja": "「〜するのに十分」。", "level": "B1", "examples": [{"en": "She's old enough to decide for herself.", "ja": "「〜するのに十分」。"}], "blank": {"before": "She's old ", "after": " to decide for herself.", "options": ["enough", "too", "so", "very"], "answer": "enough", "ja": "「〜するのに十分」。", "explain": {"answer": "enough", "why": "形容詞 + enough + to。", "opts": {}}}}, {"id": "gxf_13", "title": "as long as", "ja": "「〜する限り」= 条件。", "level": "B2", "examples": [{"en": "You can stay as long as you're quiet.", "ja": "「〜する限り」= 条件。"}], "blank": {"before": "You can stay ", "after": " long as you're quiet.", "options": ["as", "so", "too", "that"], "answer": "as", "ja": "「〜する限り」= 条件。", "explain": {"answer": "as", "why": "as long as = 条件。", "opts": {}}}}, {"id": "gxf_14", "title": "in case", "ja": "「〜する場合に備えて」。", "level": "B2", "examples": [{"en": "Take an umbrella in case it rains.", "ja": "「〜する場合に備えて」。"}], "blank": {"before": "Take an umbrella ", "after": " case it rains.", "options": ["in", "on", "at", "for"], "answer": "in", "ja": "「〜する場合に備えて」。", "explain": {"answer": "in", "why": "in case + 現在形。", "opts": {}}}}, {"id": "gxf_15", "title": "unless", "ja": "「〜しない限り」= if not。", "level": "B1", "examples": [{"en": "We'll be late unless we hurry.", "ja": "「〜しない限り」= if not。"}], "blank": {"before": "We'll be late ", "after": " we hurry.", "options": ["unless", "if", "when", "until"], "answer": "unless", "ja": "「〜しない限り」= if not。", "explain": {"answer": "unless", "why": "unless = if ... not。", "opts": {}}}}]}